Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.30,0:00:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾发生过战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.63,0:00:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战后被称为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.67,0:00:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“极光战争”的这场战乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.47,0:00:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生在赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和茵费利亚之间的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争结束之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.28,0:00:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和赛雷斯提亚便断绝交流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.68,0:00:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到今天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.45,0:00:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个世界面临即将灭亡的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.95,0:00:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身而出来拯救这场危机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.69,0:00:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是一群无名的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.44,0:02:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦   是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.71,0:02:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.74,0:02:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散华猛袭脚   双撞掌底破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.38,0:02:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.65,0:02:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好我答应你会跟她和好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.39,0:02:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.29,0:02:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第5话  歌姬们的挽歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对知识充满好奇心的我来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.94,0:02:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨清新的空气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.04,0:02:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是比任何东西还要棒的精力来源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是晶灵文明的遗迹吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一提…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.98,0:03:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座塔倒也让我挺在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇上竟然有那么大规模的遗迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在是太少见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.49,0:03:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天就去那遗迹查个究竟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.63,0:03:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.27,0:03:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.07,0:03:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨的知识之旅到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉说要事情要跟大家说哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉有事要说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.47,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们大家一起来造船吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造船？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我们总不能就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.28,0:03:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直待在这贝鲁卡纽不走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.55,0:03:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是这岛上的船只
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又因为之前的台风全部被弄坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮的巴鲁沙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.72,0:03:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又因为受了伤没办法飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才做出这个决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们用自己的双手来造船吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.50,0:03:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.73,0:03:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要造船的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是靠专门的工人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是这岛上的造船工人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都忙着重建工作没空帮我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.90,0:03:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们只有靠自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德和我负责去购买材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.81,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔就麻烦你来设计船啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那梅露蒂要做什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你负责当基尔的助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.48,0:04:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  梅露蒂会努力的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.62,0:04:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买材料这种事超麻烦一把的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.69,0:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我好不容易让我的知识好奇心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点燃了探索真理的火的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.93,0:04:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说啥东东啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您觉得如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为他们的水之大晶灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.95,0:04:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最适合用在我们伟大的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来我的领地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就更能够支撑下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.55,0:05:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用神的力量来达成报复行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.02,0:05:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.18,0:05:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好令人怀念哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.32,0:05:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看  葵吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是赛雷斯提亚耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.12,0:05:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂终于回到故乡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.13,0:05:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡里诺斯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.31,0:06:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊  卡里诺斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.17,0:06:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.72,0:06:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想回赛雷斯提亚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.06,0:06:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这设计你觉得怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.56,0:06:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂  我在问船的设计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.96,0:06:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么意见啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.46,0:06:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.00,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我设计的帆船…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“基尔·查伊贝尔号”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我是第一次设计船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过尝试做了之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.91,0:06:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才发现比想像中来的简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这艘船完成了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就又能继续旅行对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.95,0:06:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂好希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能快点回赛雷斯提亚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾   可能没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.19,0:06:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.15,0:06:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.19,0:06:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪法拉会伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为贝鲁卡纽全境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.03,0:07:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在加紧赶工造船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.77,0:07:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是主要材料的木材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.27,0:07:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,价格一下子整个飙涨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.37,0:07:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也难怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是还有上次打倒海豹时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.64,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所得到的奖金吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.44,0:07:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不太够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.31,0:07:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能够有再多一点点的钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.18,0:07:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有办法解决的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.52,0:07:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我还做了场梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.29,0:07:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦到我终于回去赛雷斯提亚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂昨天有做梦哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦到我的故乡赛雷斯提亚哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.87,0:07:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦里我还见到了卡里诺斯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡里诺斯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.17,0:07:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是抚养梅露蒂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伟大的晶灵术士哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.81,0:07:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…因为我们的钱不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.58,0:07:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在船是造不成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.75,0:07:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂觉得好难过哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那种寂寞的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.79,0:08:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微能够体会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.02,0:08:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.12,0:08:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮助梅露蒂你们吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.96,0:08:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.76,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你   可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里  包在我身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.77,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.64,0:08:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.31,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜你身上有很多钱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.68,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有冰冰凉凉又好吃的冰淇淋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人要买啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋冰淇淋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜妮玛在做什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到一个好主意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  一共是5G
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.66,0:08:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎再次惠顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…冰淇淋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.94,0:08:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜妮玛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.30,0:08:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是卡莉娜和梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.67,0:08:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一杯冰淇淋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~的   谢谢您的惠顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜你不是要吃冰吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那个钱买冰啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是有事情想请教…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁卡纽第一赚钱专家的蜜妮玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.85,0:09:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请教我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.49,0:09:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔 基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔你有没有听到我说话啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.59,0:09:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  我这绝不是偷懒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.13,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有把船重新再设计过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.97,0:09:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着那么紧张啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也没办法马上就动手造船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有看到里德和梅露蒂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到耶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正里德一定是跑去哪里睡午觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂则是去找可莉娜玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.11,0:09:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没看到玛萝妮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错   其实我是想问玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.62,0:09:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他能不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借一部份的奖金给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝你还是别去找他的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.89,0:09:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.79,0:09:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对赏金猎人来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.36,0:09:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行不过是附属品而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算人家愿意把钱借我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.56,0:09:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你要怎么还人家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.50,0:09:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.63,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.67,0:09:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.60,0:10:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是很伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.11,0:10:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两位这么缺钱用的状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.77,0:10:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经非常了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  我把这个借你们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.75,0:10:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在征求打工人员的商家名单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到那上面的店家去应征的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信老板一定会马上录用你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就有办法赚钱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.82,0:10:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打铁要趁热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.03,0:10:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜妮玛  真是谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.16,0:10:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们就赶快…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去工作赚钱吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.93,0:10:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.41,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临贝鲁卡纽餐厅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.98,0:10:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂  我们要努力打工哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.88,0:10:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.02,0:10:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  打工的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.32,0:10:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点过来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.72,0:10:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.76,0:10:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们被炒鱿鱼了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.96,0:10:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是贝鲁卡椰苏打水的试饮会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没半个人回头看一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.71,0:11:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且天气好热哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.42,0:11:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂…喉咙好干哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气热的时候果然要喝这种饮料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂喝的好饱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能再来一杯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.81,0:11:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这次的打工…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.98,0:11:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟之前的…差好多哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.38,0:11:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么认为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赚的钱也没有我们想的那么多耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社会果然没那么好混
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.90,0:12:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想到什么好主意吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.24,0:12:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把这社会的严苛性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写成诗歌把它朗诵出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~虽然我们不停的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所得的酬劳却丝毫不增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.71,0:12:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.28,0:12:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是应征兼职人员的广告吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.45,0:12:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写了些什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.92,0:12:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请至夜间俱乐部“三重奏”…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  真是一把好琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.27,0:14:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.61,0:14:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…你的声音真美耶  小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是真心赞美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.08,0:14:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我向你说声谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.98,0:14:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想泡我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.68,0:14:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会听进去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的把戏被人家识破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.32,0:14:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那首歌…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我年轻的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这贝鲁卡纽很流行的一首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是在这个岛出生的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.06,0:14:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来…你该不会是救…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店内的各位宾客请注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要开始本店精彩的歌舞秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位尽情的观赏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.20,0:15:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅长歌唱的卡莉娜的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.87,0:15:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…明日之星的梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AND可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为各位带来的表演！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.83,0:15:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太佩服自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.00,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱的好啊  梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我啊  梅露蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.13,0:16:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都不说我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.14,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.91,0:16:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  之前说好的打工费
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.01,0:16:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦请马上支付给我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.38,0:16:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.48,0:16:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们没陪客人喝酒的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.38,0:16:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不能支付打工费的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂可没听到你这么说过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.49,0:16:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子小妹妹你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.06,0:16:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很受那些客人的欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜托你去坐一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.40,0:16:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请不要这样！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要过来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.90,0:16:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的好  葵吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.17,0:16:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.91,0:16:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用抓的也要把你抓出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.74,0:16:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.58,0:16:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是小孩子来的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回旅馆去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.55,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.99,0:16:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在这个岛出生的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种离国境偏远的小岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会是我的家乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.77,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事…事情好像变得很不妙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.67,0:17:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  这次是换演戏吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的店家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止你这样子的客人出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有雇用厉害的高手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说保镖是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.02,0:17:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.75,0:17:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大师轮到你出场了！大师！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.33,0:17:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.50,0:17:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻烦你收拾掉他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.70,0:17:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.67,0:17:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会跑来当保镖啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.07,0:17:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细情形等一下再跟你解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.24,0:17:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…我已经收了他的订金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能不能请你输给我呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.74,0:17:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是要我配合你演戏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦  装装样子就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.35,0:17:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.58,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.08,0:17:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是演戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.35,0:18:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打输对我来说也是很没面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.62,0:18:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是装个样子有什么关系嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.19,0:18:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会没关系！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.59,0:18:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小气鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.02,0:18:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要输啊里德大师！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得好  再打激烈一点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.26,0:18:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐你也不要输啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.56,0:18:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德大人和玛萝妮小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.47,0:18:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下糟了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫法拉小姐过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给梅露蒂你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.71,0:18:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明事理的家伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.01,0:18:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.21,0:18:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.01,0:18:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.95,0:18:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂妮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.69,0:18:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经吾水之医治来保护汝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  梅露蒂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在里德跟玛萝妮在打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.80,0:18:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相望你能帮帮忙好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对人类的战斗一点兴趣也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温蒂妮拜托你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.94,0:19:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你   温蒂妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.92,0:19:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.62,0:19:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那家店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.93,0:19:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.37,0:19:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们竟然在那种酒店里惹事生非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.24,0:19:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.61,0:19:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要那么大声啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.94,0:19:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们三个是为了赚买木材的钱啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.28,0:19:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.12,0:19:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.25,0:19:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂  可莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.46,0:19:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是被你们打败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.99,0:19:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还真是乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.66,0:19:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过非常谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉   法拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.73,0:19:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德和梅露蒂\N可莉娜所赚的钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然数目并不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.67,0:19:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只要能增加身上的钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.04,0:20:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有足够的钱购买木材了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.17,0:20:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样里德他们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.88,0:20:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了重新踏上旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便开始动手造船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.75,0:20:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底他们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法从这个贝鲁卡纽出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.92,0:20:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新他们的旅程吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.99,0:20:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定能会去赛雷斯提亚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.79,0:20:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待下回精彩好戏


